metadata.name: Galactic Fold
metadata.description: Galactic Fold  NFT Collection, featuring 101 one-of-a-kind digital gems inspired by the beauty of the cosmos. Each NFT is a unique and stunning representation of a celestial wonder, from sparkling stars to vibrant nebulae. With "Galactic Fold" you'll own a piece of the universe's majesty in the form of a beautiful and collectible digital asset.
